<tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udethiel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dethiel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/2/01 5:32:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: White Dragonscale Boots</span><hr size=1> I did the quest with high amiable.  (somewhere in the amiable range is where the quest is attainable, I know people who are lower amiable who cannot get a response other than the &quot;get away from me slime&quot; response)<br><br>These quests are designed so that once you recieve the actual quest response from a mob you have enough faction.  Make sure you can get the full response from him (give the phrase I can't remember and he says &quot;.....bring me the head of tormax and I shall reward you...&quot; (wish I could remember key phrase for that, because it took me like 10 mins to figure it out standing there and it's a pain in tha ass) and hand it over.  He will give you the griffon sword, and a huge faction + (went to ally)  give him the sword and get the boots. (I have heard there is a third item and that the quest is circular so you get sword back again for turning that in, but I wasn't about to try)<br><br>Go and get your boots! <p><img src=http://www.legacyofsorrow.net/mj/dethiel-sig.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udejah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dejah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/2/01 9:01:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: White Dragonscale Boots</span><hr size=1> Thank you for your response!<br><br>This is good news indeed. Yelinak does in fact tell me to bring the head of Tormax to him.<br><br>*crosses fingers* and is off to SS..<br><br>Dejah<br>Sorcerer Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udejah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dejah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/2/01 12:15:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: White Dragonscale Boots</span><hr size=1> It worked. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>Sooo, to conclude, if one can get Yelinak to tell him/her to bring the Tormax head, one can get the boots.<br><br>Did go up to kindly, maybe they lowered the faction gain from the quest.<br><br>Dejah<br>Sorcerer Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udethiel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dethiel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/2/01 7:02:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: White Dragonscale Boots</span><hr size=1> Grats <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Yeah, they tend to play around with a lot of the faction adjustments still it seems.  Dar brood shroud used to be huge faction, but my friend did today and didn't even move up one notch <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>Enjoy those boots, as I know you will.  Only 1 other item I know of with that much mana on it in the game and it is extremely rare and has no FT.  And of course, these are BOOTS heehee. <p><img src=http://www.legacyofsorrow.net/mj/dethiel-sig.gif></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=362.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=362.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=362.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=362.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=362.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=362.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notificatio